      "Case Complaint Summary": {
        "value": "The complaint was filed by Plaintiff Trexis Insurance Corporation against Defendants Kenneth C. Stogner, McNichols Trucking, LLC, Ethan Daniels, Jennifer Daniels as mother and next friend of Ethan Daniels, and Dalen Norris. Trexis is an out- of-state insurance company authorized to conduct business in Arkansas. The complaint arises from a July 31, 2023 motor vehicle accident involving a 2017 Dodge Charger reported stolen by Roy Hamilton and a 2018 Freightliner truck operated by Defendant Stogner",
